title: Special Preview - Up On Game with LaVar Arrington, T.J. Houshmandzadeh and Plaxico Burress -Fixing The Dallas Cowboys
itunes:title: Special Preview - Up On Game with LaVar Arrington, T.J. Houshmandzadeh and Plaxico Burress -Fixing The Dallas Cowboys
description:
LaVar Arrington, T.J. Houshmandzadeh and Plaxico Burress try to fix the Dallas Cowboys by giving Jerry Jones some advice on what to do in the first round of the upcoming NFL Draft. The Lakers and Nets might be on a collision course to meet in the NBA Finals but which team needs their stars more in order to get there?
